    {
      "type": "talk_mult",
      "npc": "narrator",
      "lines": [
        "\"It is precisely because nothing matters",
        "that you have no reason not to do those little things.",
        "helping someone.",
        "improving another's life.",
        "Time spent living in meaninglessness",
        "is not wasted.\""
